 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-phone-heading font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2\">Contact</h3><!-- AI-CONTENT: contact-phone | Replace with practice phone number. --><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-phone-text text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-sans\">Phone: (555) 123-4567</p><!-- AI-CONTENT: contact-email | Replace with practice email address. --><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-email-text text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-sans\">Email: info@example.com</p></div></div><!-- Opening Hours --><div class=\"flex items-start gap-5\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-primary-subtle\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 md:w-7 md:h-7 text-primary\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-hours-heading font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3\">Opening Hours</h3><!-- AI-CONTENT: contact-hours | Replace each day/time pair with practice business hours. --><div class=\"grid gap-y-2 text-gray-600 font-sans grid-cols-[auto_1fr]\"><span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-hours-row-1-day font-medium text-gray-900 pr-6\">Mon - Fri</span><span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-hours-row-1-time\">8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</span><span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-hours-row-2-day font-medium text-gray-900 pr-6\">Saturday</span><span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-contact-content-component-hours-row-2-time\">9:00 AM 